\c 11
\s Dhavhidhi anovimba naMwari,
\s nokuti anochengeta vakarurama
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Ndinovimba naJehovha; Munoreva seiko kumweya wangu, muchiti, "Tizira kugomo rako seshiri?
\v 2 Nokuti, tarira, vakaipa vanowembura uta, Vanogadzira museve wavo parukungiso, Kuti vafure anomwoyo wakarurama parima.
\v 3 Kana nheyo dzakaparadzwa, Akarurama angaiteiko?"
\v 4 Jehovha uri mutemberi yake tsvene, Iye Jehovha, chigaro chake chohushe chiri kudenga;
\s Meso ake anotarira, mafungiro
\s ameso ake anoidza vana vavanhu.
\p
\v 5 Jehovha anoidza vakarurama; Asi mweya wake unovenga wakaipa neanomanikidza.
\p
\v 6 Achanisira misungo pamusoro pavakaipa;
\s Moto nesuriferi nemhepo inopisa, ndiwo uchava mukombe wavo wavakagoverwa.
\p
\v 7 Nokuti Jehovha akarurama; anoda zvakarurama;
\s Vakarurama vachaona chiso chake.
